{"tid":1866364,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"搶唔到口罩？全球人口清洗？！","createTime":"2020-02-06T16:59:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-06T17:15:12.000Z","uid":298751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"5a4e09eac001b844b618cd1b5b18930f257a669c","tid":1866364,"uid":298751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T16:59:24.000Z","msg":"李幾日反思咗少少嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nBTW 頭先pepe 0.5秒就蒸發了200盒口罩，10分鐘就搶走哂1000套裝<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />認真可怕<br />\n<br />\n<strong></strong>有咩「手技」可以傳授下<strong></strong><br />\n<br />\n中國係咪摺唔埋野味檔，順便減少人口，所以洩漏P4 人為病毒，然後確診人數到咁上下大，就提高致命率，以確保死得夠多人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n第二<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n中國境內 <br />\n包括I湖北市為武漢肺炎爆發地，死亡人數肯定「上面」唔比講，求其維持2.1%死亡率比公眾睇<br />\nⅡ旁邊湖南禽流感殺二萬幾隻雞，雞肉唔知會唔會流入香港<br />\n <br />\n至於美國，爆流感死咗萬幾人，睇落有5位數字好似好多<br />\n<br />\n但流感+武漢肺炎係77億人口當中，可能死唔到0.01%<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n第三<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n啲人成日都話地球滅絕可能係行星撞🌍<br />\n但話唔定人類未必係比科技玩死自己（發現到啲唔應知道的事實）<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">係有可能比病毒主宰生命，中國人會唔會食抗生素希望醫到肺炎</span></strong>，我覺得一定有人咁做<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n若果條友死唔去，又或者受抗生素影響而變異的肺炎被傳開去，會唔會係生化武器（浣熊市？）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nP牌仔第一次開post，9up幾句<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2cf695b16837699044056febeed2db0cf279446","tid":1866364,"uid":242537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T17:12:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zhgxPkB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzhgxPkB.jpg&h=2da7bea5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7d5166b94baeaa020f4d150cf40b825a7348de8a","tid":1866364,"uid":281159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"